The week did not turn on a single order or speech. It unfolded instead as a series of decisions that, taken together, showed a government more willing to use every lever at hand\'97funding, law enforcement, data, and even museums\'97to protect itself and punish those outside its circle. The pattern was not new, but it was more settled. What had once looked like improvisation now read as method.\
